      "dual_dialogue_group": null,
      "dual_dialogue_side": null,
      "element_id": "el-00001"
    },
    {
      "kind": "Action",
      "text": "A gorgeous day.  The sun is shining.  But BRICK BRADDOCK, retired police detective, is sitting quietly, contemplating -- something.",
      "starts_new_page": false,
      "scene_number": null,
      "block_kind": null,
      "block_id": null,
      "dual_dialogue_group": null,
      "dual_dialogue_side": null,
      "element_id": "el-00002"
    },
    {
      "kind": "Action",
      "text": "The SCREEN DOOR slides open and DICK STEEL, his former partner and fellow retiree, emerges with two cold beers.",
      "starts_new_page": false,
      "scene_number": null,
      "block_kind": null,
      "block_id": null,
      "dual_dialogue_group": null,
      "dual_dialogue_side": null,
      "element_id": "el-00003"
    },
    {
      "kind": "Character",
      "text": "STEEL",
      "starts_new_page": false,
      "scene_number": null,
      "block_kind": "DialogueBlock",
      "block_id": "block-00001",
      "dual_dialogue_group": null,
      "dual_dialogue_side": null,
      "element_id": "el-00004"
    },
    {
      "kind": "Dialogue",
      "text": "Beer's ready!",
      "starts_new_page": false,
      "scene_number": null,
      "block_kind": "DialogueBlock",
      "block_id": "block-00001",
      "dual_dialogue_group": null,
      "dual_dialogue_side": null,
      "element_id": "el-00005"
    },
    {
      "kind": "Character",
      "text": "BRICK",
      "starts_new_page": false,
      "scene_number": null,
      "block_kind": "DialogueBlock",
      "block_id": "block-00002",
      "dual_dialogue_group": null,
      "dual_dialogue_side": null,
      "element_id": "el-00006"
    },
    {
      "kind": "Dialogue",
      "text": "Are they cold?",
      "starts_new_page": false,
      "scene_number": null,
      "block_kind": "DialogueBlock",
      "block_id": "block-00002",
      "dual_dialogue_group": null,
      "dual_dialogue_side": null,
      "element_id": "el-00007"
    },
    {
      "kind": "Character",
      "text": "STEEL",
      "starts_new_page": false,
      "scene_number": null,
      "block_kind": "DialogueBlock",
      "block_id": "block-00003",
      "dual_dialogue_group": null,
      "dual_dialogue_side": null,
      "element_id": "el-00008"
    },
    {
      "kind": "Dialogue",
      "text": "Does a bear crap in the woods?",
      "starts_new_page": false,
      "scene_number": null,
      "block_kind": "DialogueBlock",
      "block_id": "block-00003",
      "dual_dialogue_group": null,
      "dual_dialogue_side": null,
      "element_id": "el-00009"
    },
    {
      "kind": "Action",
      "text": "Steel sits.  They laugh at the dumb joke.",
      "starts_new_page": false,
      "scene_number": null,
      "block_kind": null,
      "block_id": null,
      "dual_dialogue_group": null,
      "dual_dialogue_side": null,
      "element_id": "el-00010"
    },
    {
      "kind": "Character",
      "text": "STEEL",
      "starts_new_page": false,
      "scene_number": null,
      "block_kind": "DialogueBlock",
      "block_id": "block-00004",
      "dual_dialogue_group": null,
      "dual_dialogue_side": null,
      "element_id": "el-00011"
    },
    {
      "kind": "Parenthetical",
      "text": "(beer raised)",
      "starts_new_page": false,
      "scene_number": null,
      "block_kind": "DialogueBlock",
      "block_id": "block-00004",
      "dual_dialogue_group": null,
      "dual_dialogue_side": null,
      "element_id": "el-00012"
    },
    {
      "kind": "Dialogue",
      "text": "To retirement.",
      "starts_new_page": false,
      "scene_number": null,
      "block_kind": "DialogueBlock",
      "block_id": "block-00004",
      "dual_dialogue_group": null,
      "dual_dialogue_side": null,
      "element_id": "el-00013"
    },
    {
      "kind": "Character",
      "text": "BRICK",
      "starts_new_page": false,
      "scene_number": null,
      "block_kind": "DialogueBlock",
      "block_id": "block-00005",
      "dual_dialogue_group": null,
      "dual_dialogue_side": null,
      "element_id": "el-00014"
    },
    {
      "kind": "Dialogue",
      "text": "To retirement.",
      "starts_new_page": false,
      "scene_number": null,
      "block_kind": "DialogueBlock",
      "block_id": "block-00005",
      "dual_dialogue_group": null,
      "dual_dialogue_side": null,
      "element_id": "el-00015"
    },
    {
      "kind": "Action",
      "text": "They drink long and well from the beers.",
      "starts_new_page": false,
      "scene_number": null,
      "block_kind": null,
      "block_id": null,
      "dual_dialogue_group": null,
      "dual_dialogue_side": null,
      "element_id": "el-00016"
    },
    {
      "kind": "Action",
      "text": "And then there's a long beat.\nLonger than is funny.\nLong enough to be depressing.",
      "starts_new_page": false,
      "scene_number": null,
      "block_kind": null,
      "block_id": null,
      "dual_dialogue_group": null,
      "dual_dialogue_side": null,
      "element_id": "el-00017"
    },
    {
      "kind": "Action",
      "text": "The men look at each other.",
      "starts_new_page": false,
      "scene_number": null,
      "block_kind": null,
      "block_id": null,
      "dual_dialogue_group": null,
      "dual_dialogue_side": null,
      "element_id": "el-00018"
    },
    {
      "kind": "Character",
      "text": "STEEL",
      "starts_new_page": false,
